  "rollout_plan_displayname": "Will ship enabled for all users",
  "motivation": "Chrome has announced that the current approach to third-party cookies will be maintained. Given this, we expect adoption to decrease over time as cross-site measurement will remain possible in Chrome using third-party cookies.\n\nFurther, other browser engines have not signaled interest in launching the API. Removing this (and other Privacy Sandbox APIs) will help focus efforts on the proposed interoperable Attribution standard.\n\nSee also https://privacysandbox.com/news/update-on-plans-for-privacy-sandbox-technologies/.\n",
